-- NEW FEATURES --

* Create a race object
	- Simple race engine to find winner (for now the algorithm will be, RAND(), then work on Dice rolls, - eventually work from odds / distance / horse stats / jockey etc)
* allow user to bet money
* when race complete, pay any necessary winnings to the winners (cron? button?)
* store race results from horses
	- Generate odds based on last race

* races have distance - horses with longer stamina would be better
* horses of 2 years only race other 2 year old horses (and only short distances)
* races will have maximum weight limits
* races should have an age limit

